title: Home Page
text: Hi, I’m Michelle Le and welcome to my personal website. I’ve created this website through coding skills I’ve honed during two semesters of bioinformatics at my alma mater, UMass Amherst. No, my major wasn’t in computer science if that’s what you’re wondering. I currently have a B.S in biology, but I choose to code on the side as a fun little hobby.
